window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>If Punisher and Batman had a baby raised by John Wick....</p> <p>How far would you go to see justice done? How far is too far? For Madisun, the answer is simple. There are people in this world who need killing, and she's just the woman for the job!</p> <p>From the best-selling author of the Full Metal Superhero books comes an exciting new ongoing series set in the same world as <i>Arsenal</i>.</p>"; 
